20#ifndef GCC_BB_REORDER
21#define GCC_BB_REORDER
22
23/* Target-specific globals. */
24struct target_bb_reorder {
25 /* Length of unconditional jump instruction. */
26 int x_uncond_jump_length;
27};
28
29extern struct target_bb_reorder default_target_bb_reorder;
30#if SWITCHABLE_TARGET
31extern struct target_bb_reorder *this_target_bb_reorder;
32#else
33#define this_target_bb_reorder (&default_target_bb_reorder)
34#endif
35
36extern int get_uncond_jump_length (void);
37
38extern void insert_section_boundary_note (void);
39
40#endif
